        <abstract>
            <para>The dataset consists of occurrence data of the aquatic organism groups fish, macroinvertebrates and macrophytes that were sampled in the German federal state Saxony between 2007 and 2011. The sampling was conducted according to the protocols of the national monitoring programme for implementation of the Water Framework Directive.</para>
<para>For additional metadata see: http://data.freshwaterbiodiversity.eu/metadb/bf_mdb_view.php?entryID&amp;#61;BFE_93</para>
        </abstract>
